A dynamic illustration of a brightly colored, slightly whimsical instant card titled "School Buddies," depicting a diverse group of children – some smiling and offering healing hands (representing friends), while others are depicted with a grimace and a cup, implying they’ve been forced to drink, set in a vibrant schoolyard with cartoonish trees and buildings, painted in a style reminiscent of classic Magic The Gathering art, bright and saturated colors, 8k, detailed.